Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  已經慢我一圈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓住咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  這是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的  已經不礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續跑吧  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第3話\N黑和藍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽將近  早上和午休都要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了節省時間  午飯就在這裡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把便當都帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為練習做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要比平常的多一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚啊  一眼就看出在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是所有人都要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在午休就有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  這是針對你的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要你這樣的初學者直接去參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在短時間內加強鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  大家都會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠也會對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到這  大家換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們去訂購護具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餡料中使用北海道產紅豆慢工制出的極品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用吹彈可破般的糯米皮料包裹住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的甜味中參雜著淡淡鹹味搭配出絕妙的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  老師  你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新部員入部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我看看竹劍和護具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請便請便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  都這麼久了你也讓我再去指導一下部員的練習嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…再說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是有段數的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我曾拜託他擔任教練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就進入狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就好像電視劇裡面的熱血教師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家練到都站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後帶著完成使命的男人的笑容離去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是…很棒的笑容啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之後被部員臭罵的人是我啊！這誰受得了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我什麼時候再去好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這個…坂口先生也很忙吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很閒哦  很閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了閒再沒別的了  真是遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且讓強一些的人來指導對部員也比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  以前你怎麼樣我是不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在是沒有在練習了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我每週都有去道場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要取得好成績的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  坂口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這裡的部員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你平日的指導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代我向你爸爸問好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是竹劍  其他人也隨便看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要買38了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三八是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉喲！這傢伙是個糊塗鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說竹劍的種類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長度是三尺八寸  所以簡稱38
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的正式戰中不用這個是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算長度差不多一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但重量就區別很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要自己掂量好了挑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然親手揮一下來確認是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的豆大福…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有木刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護具…選哪個都無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子因為有胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微選大一點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你這是性騷擾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！這不是事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這個！好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個很貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下手印！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  給你獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在制服上套護具真白癡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:29.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是都說了嗎  那樣吃的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  聽我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福我算是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔可是有些硬來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我還真要感謝你加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然家裡還有道場  也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是為了正義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因為我認為這樣做是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會認真對待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我會儘快送過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了  那就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆大福真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡皮更厚一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月一定能比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我要是贏了怎麼辦還沒決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  看來我不做點什麼也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要拿走裝飾在你房間裡的那樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾在我房間裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最珍視的…那樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是Super Famicom嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スーファミ：スーパーファミコン(Super Famicom)的簡稱，\N任天堂於1990年發行的遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是獎盃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎盃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本來就是我的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了你就把它還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在也不能再互相對戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我們的學生決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒拿來裝飾房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是混在搬家的行李中帶來了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  前輩  我僥倖打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  無論是僥倖還是運氣  結果就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你贏了  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  我就要畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前比一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩你不是都引退了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為不甘心輸給這麼僥倖的我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就用獎盃作賭注…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這回事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的獎盃你有好好收著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我贏了  你就給我獎盃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那時候那麼說  前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道中沒有僥倖和運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要比你強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話這東西對我來說根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}練習目錄！\N這是小都都的\N加油咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～真像部長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們劍道部也漸漸正式化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鞘發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她差不多也該回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為最強的選手了  接下來是「哦！小都都」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！我死了算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞘子你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是沒有才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧…小說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞘子！這麼晚你上哪去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天才！是天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日本第一！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是天才所以我辦得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  她老是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  榮花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂購的竹劍送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的時候來部團教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（領隊在視聽教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  這是不是紀梨乃前輩寫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}給勇次和其他人\N竹內\N來了哦\N紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（竹內、因為發音和日文竹劍相同所以寫成了這樣的別字）]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹內是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（內有竹刀）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大中午就來練習  開什麼玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是太放不開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找個人來發洩一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個一年級的應該也已經不去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再去教訓教訓他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去社團露個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  不揍個人我消不了氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防具送到了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各自去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是儘快把錢交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢可以交給老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我先保管著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先保管？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你們這些不信任的眼光算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  大家來試帶護具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先保管？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會亂用啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會私吞的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怎麼戴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮花  不能先戴頭盔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  首先繫好腰垂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頸繩也要自己繫好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上手套就不能繫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像七五三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（七五三是日本獨特的節日，可以看作是兒童節一樣的存在）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你也買了新護具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  你家不是開道場的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都買了  所以我也想要新的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的護具已經很舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上第一次參加部團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以覺得道具也一起換新比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你是紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！這是為了打倒前輩的隊伍所聚集起來的正義戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而領隊  紅色就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那我這個部長呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給人的角色感覺就是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼角色感覺啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那麼小都都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然是粉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好像一瞬間看到黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是藍色的鞘子和還沒找到的綠色！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將五個人召集在我石田司令麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一定會贏得勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就那麼在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是女生太不公平了  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊？你果然還是黃色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不全都成黃色了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦  這樣的戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  男生們就在暗中支持女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說藍色還沒有復活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她還在請假期間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  前段時間有發「我要死了」的簡訊來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這不糟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  常有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  早晚會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一年級的  來戴上名布看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插到腰垂那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  粉紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎的名布…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「榮花」而變成「榮光」了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在店裡寫的字太醜  所以才搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…我們再買新的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  而且這樣更帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊！可以看到閃耀著無意義的金光哦！金光！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉哦  今天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？是今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為突然被拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得給大家說一聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我會給你打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣  任性的女孩子也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…前段時間的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會經過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前雖然看到過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  安下心來慢慢等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要帶小都都來哦  段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是最需要練習的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我會跟她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡  這點根本不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩劍道根本沒成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是小鞘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管她的  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為刹車失靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你！這樣也太過分了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還是初學者  但是劍道真是很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問有什麼有趣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用棒子打人敲人揍人  而且還都是合法的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}viva violence{\r}\N暴力萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面都能受到鍛煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想像一下對方痛苦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的S心就蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習團隊合作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人也得到成長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說回來只要我有了段郎就什麼都可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下回是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「粉紅和藍」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M的傢伙一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說記得給老娘看！
